analysis: The agent failed to call the appropriate tool after receiving all necessary information from the user, instead responding with a meta-comment about API/server issues, thus not attempting the expected function call or analysis.

The agent incorrectly capitalized the values for "investmentSize" and "marketDynamics" in the function call; the expected values are lowercase ("moderate", "dynamic"), so the evaluator did not recognize the function call as a valid match.
The agent incorrectly specified the "outputDetail" parameter as "Detailed" instead of the expected "Summary," resulting in a function call that did not match the evaluator's required signature.

The agent failed to invoke the required function to generate the coverage report and instead responded with an irrelevant error message about network issues, demonstrating a lack of tool use despite the user's clarified request.
The agent used an invalid value ("Comprehensive") for the "detailLevel" parameter instead of the required "Detailed", resulting in a mismatch with the expected function call.

The agent incorrectly included an extra "weatherDetail" argument not supported by the FlightStatus_checkFlightAndWeather function, resulting in a parameter mismatch and failure to invoke the function as specified by the API.
The agent omitted the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter in the function call, failing to specify that only games with good ratings should be recommended as requested by the user.
